text: Hew Dalrymple may refer to: * Hew Dalrymple, Lord North Berwick (1652–1737), Scottish judge and politician * Sir Hew Dalrymple, 2nd Baronet (1712–1790), Scottish politician, grandson of the above * Hew Dalrymple (advocate) (c. 1740–1774), Scottish advocate, poet and Attorney-General of Grenada * Sir Hew Dalrymple, 3rd Baronet (1746–1800), Scottish politician, son of the 2nd Baronet * Hew Whitefoord Dalrymple (1750–1830), British Army general * Hew Hamilton Dalrymple (1857–1945), Scottish politician
